Text.text: Ominous Goblet - A symbolism of foresight that comes at a certain price.
Cordelia Flower - A breathtaking flower that reacts to a certain emotion.
Promise Ring - An artifact containing one's promises and memories.
Eternal Runestone - A powerful stone capable of sealing one's fate within.
Guiding Compass - An artifact with a large arrow that points its direction to "home".
Priceless Timepiece - An indicator of time, one that brings assurance to the people.
